startLearnMore:
would you like to learn more about the world?;
- Y or N
    - if Y, run, then run startTutorial;
    - if N, run startTutorial;
    - if something else, state incorrect and run startLearnMore again;

startTutorial:
would you like to start the tutorial?;
- Y or N
    - if Y, run, then run startGame;
    - if N, run startGame;
    - if something else, state incorrect and run startTutorial again;

